## Ingress: Cloudflare Tunnel

All traffic arrives via a Cloudflare Tunnel ("thjread-vm" in the Cloudflare
account); nginx publishes NO host ports. cloudflared runs as a compose
service; its token lives in /home/thjread/.env (TUNNEL_TOKEN=..., chmod 600,
not in git). DNS: thjread.com / www / reminders are proxied CNAMEs to
<tunnel-id>.cfargotunnel.com. Tunnel ingress maps all hostnames to
http://nginx:8081 (plain-HTTP vhost; TLS terminates at the Cloudflare edge).
The old 443 origin-pull setup (ssl.conf, certs/) is still in the nginx image
but unused - can be removed eventually.

